sections.text:
An example of a National Codex Committee could include representatives from the following institutions:
i. Relevant Ministries/Government institutions such as:
- Ministry of Health;
- Ministry of Agriculture, Fisheries and Livestock;
- Ministry of Trade and Industry;
- Ministry of Environment;

