sections.text:
The basic requirements for a Codex Contact Point may include the following:
- committed staff;
- code of conduct;
- adequate office space;
- communication facilities, e.g. telephone, fax, e-mail, postal address, etc.;
- stationery;
- printing and photocopying equipment, e.g. computer, printer, photocopier, etc.

